You have the following MCP servers at your disposal. Use them generously.


github: use this to search code repos on github to find similar code snippets that could be useful for the given task.


perplexity-ask: use this to get a deep summarized search of the web that included social media and youtube as sources.


brave: use this as the default go-to web search tool.

playwright: use this as the default go-to browser use tool.


context7: use this as the default programming language documentation tool. this contains thousands of the most common up-to-date libraries for many languages